thread.title: Customer

author: Customer
title: Customer
text: I've always had nothing but great experiences with Onnit and as a Joe Rogan and Aubrey Marcus fan I'm probably a little bit bias. However, the products are fantastic I own a few shirts and have tried a bunch of supplements. The only reason I give it a 4 instead of a 5 is because the products are just too expensive for a college student like me. Otherwise awesome company and products!
